WEBVTT

00:08.588 --> 00:10.616
<i>Previously on</i> One Dollar...

00:10.641 --> 00:11.928
<i>It was a guy in a...</i>

00:11.995 --> 00:13.746
in a dark <i>hoodie, and...</i>

00:13.793 --> 00:15.114
<i>Where were you? Near the mill?</i>

00:15.139 --> 00:16.196
<i>No.</i>

00:16.248 --> 00:17.495
Where were you, then?

00:17.556 --> 00:18.836
<i>Look, you can probably imagine</i>

00:18.875 --> 00:19.929
<i>what case I'm working.</i>

00:19.954 --> 00:22.016
- What is this?
- You came to the ER the other night.

00:22.041 --> 00:23.101
I just wanted to drop by,

00:23.126 --> 00:24.428
<i>make sure you really hurt your head</i>

00:24.453 --> 00:26.390
<i>riding your four-wheeler
at 3:00 in the morning.</i>

00:26.530 --> 00:28.032
Walmart.

00:28.078 --> 00:29.382
You know who Travis Wilcox is?

00:29.407 --> 00:30.428
He came by,

00:30.453 --> 00:31.488
four different occasions,

00:31.513 --> 00:32.870
and bought shovels off me.

00:32.910 --> 00:34.546
That's the guy.

00:36.662 --> 00:38.903
Are you here about the
babysitting flyer?

00:38.976 --> 00:40.177
Come on in.

00:40.217 --> 00:42.196
I guess the most important question...

00:42.241 --> 00:44.563
are-are you free tomorrow night?

00:45.100 --> 00:46.808
<i>Do you have a schoolteacher discount?</i>

00:46.833 --> 00:48.003
I gotta make a profit,

00:48.028 --> 00:49.387
no matter how big my heart is.

00:49.467 --> 00:50.541
It's a terrible burden,

00:50.566 --> 00:51.604
having a heart that big.

00:51.638 --> 00:52.898
Seven.

