Keep you alive.

39:20.489 --> 39:22.326
Chewy isn't a big fan of black people.

39:22.351 --> 39:23.680
True, but it's also true

39:23.705 --> 39:25.187
that Chewy's just an all-around asshole

39:25.212 --> 39:27.140
- who likes to needle rookies.
- Not only that,

39:27.165 --> 39:28.750
he's got problems working with a woman.

39:28.783 --> 39:31.287
Yet and still he's got to protect you.

39:32.173 --> 39:34.557
Chewy said you and Trask were friends.

39:35.266 --> 39:36.776
Yep. True and good friends.

39:36.801 --> 39:39.438
Until you had a fight
about the missing girl.

39:39.835 --> 39:41.663
Abby Washington. That's right.

39:41.749 --> 39:43.991
Did you really call the
Chief a racist fuck?

39:44.079 --> 39:46.498
Peter told me to drop the case and I...

39:47.124 --> 39:49.993
Well, nothing stings a white man
like being called a racist.

39:50.339 --> 39:51.954
Chief's the one who treats me the best.

39:51.979 --> 39:53.814
Seems like he really
wants me to do well.

39:53.839 --> 39:55.460
Yeah, I'm sure he really does.

39:55.485 --> 39:57.237
He's no Chewy; he knows better.

39:57.340 --> 40:00.142
But he still gives Bud Carl
the benefit of the doubt.

40:00.455 --> 40:02.347
And a missing black girl...

40:02.427 --> 40:03.971
well, I worry that doesn't bother Peter

40:03.996 --> 40:06.087
quite as much as a missing white girl.

40:07.663 --> 40:09.665
I hear that.

40:11.520 --> 40:13.054
I'll see you.

40:13.169 --> 40:14.564
All right.

40:18.602 --> 40:20.301
But you can't quit.

40:20.414 --> 40:21.887
We've got two more weeks.

40:21.912 --> 40:23.081
I have to.

40:23.318 --> 40:25.521
You reported the incident immediately

40:25.740 --> 40:28.677
and I spoke at length with
Markell and his father.

40:29.412 --> 40:32.160
You can't quit because you got angry.

40:32.329 --> 40:33.936
- If every teacher quit because...
- I hit him.

40:33.961 --> 40:35.520
I spanked him. I-I mean,

40:35.545 --> 40:36.810
I've never hit a kid before.

40:36.999 --> 40:38.238
You lost your patience.

40:39.595 --> 40:40.784
It happens to all of us.

40:40.809 --> 40:43.055
You think I don't know what
losing my patience feels like?

40:43.086 --> 40:45.988
38 years, I've never come
close to hitting a kid.

40:46.122 --> 40:48.992
And that is why I cannot
accept your resignation.

40:52.040 --> 40:55.118
Why do you see this one
misstep as so final?

40:57.993 --> 40:59.994
Because I...

41:03.516 --> 41:05.814
I don't know.

41:06.286 --> 41:09.887
Because what I did is
beyond the pale and...

41:10.833 --> 41:13.284
- that's it.
- Hmm.

41:14.463 --> 41:16.025
Carol, I didn't want to bring this up,

41:16.050 --> 41:17.431
but Nikki saw the incident.

41:17.456 --> 41:18.657
Oh, I know.

41:18.682 --> 41:20.406
And she wondered...

41:21.104 --> 41:24.039
- She thought maybe...
- What?

41:24.665 --> 41:27.451
Do you think that Markell's
race played a part in it?

41:27.649 --> 41:29.191
Oh, my God. No.

41:29.244 --> 41:30.981
I'm-I'm...

41:31.420 --> 41:32.881
No, I'm not a racist.

41:32.906 --> 41:34.258
I mean, I've taught
many black children.

41:34.282 --> 41:36.134
Some of the students I'm proudest of

41:36.651 --> 41:38.922
were black... are black. That's...

41:38.947 --> 41:41.416
- I'm not saying...
- Of course.

41:41.856 --> 41:44.893
But let's just stop and look at this.

41:44.927 --> 41:46.695
Okay.

41:46.781 --> 41:51.453
These other African-American
kids, your former students,

41:51.659 --> 41:53.828
they weren't difficult, were they?

41:54.036 --> 41:57.410
Uh, I would... some of
them were difficult.

41:57.492 --> 42:00.061
I-I don't think of it that
way, anyway... difficult.

42:00.275 --> 42:01.512
That's... but the point is,

42:01.537 --> 42:02.972
I've-I've taught all kinds of kids

42:02.997 --> 42:04.332
with all kinds of behaviors.

42:04.357 --> 42:06.325
I've never done anything
like this before.

42:06.562 --> 42:08.432
And I don't know what you're
saying, anyway. I mean

42:08.457 --> 42:10.754
, if I am a racist that's worse.
You should fire me.

42:10.779 --> 42:13.850
Unacknowledged bias
exists in all of us.

42:14.805 --> 42:17.151
Now, the solution isn't
to throw in the towel.

42:17.226 --> 42:19.795
Something like this
should be a wake-up call,

42:19.820 --> 42:22.248
an opportunity to look inside yourself.

42:22.336 --> 42:23.545
If that's what's inside me,

42:23.570 --> 42:25.786
I don't want to know about it.

42:26.368 --> 42:27.833
I'm sorry. I am...

42:27.858 --> 42:29.641
I'm... I am very sorry.

42:29.666 --> 42:31.083
Um...

42:32.087 --> 42:34.073
I just think it's time.

42:35.317 --> 42:39.227
If you really feel this bad, go.

42:39.862 --> 42:43.055
Take the summer, but
don't quit teaching.

42:43.245 --> 42:46.115
You are one of the best
teachers I've ever seen.

42:47.689 --> 42:49.713
Just call it a break

42:49.838 --> 42:51.737
and you'll come back fresh in the fall.

42:54.035 --> 42:56.048
My daughter in California
is always begging me

42:56.073 --> 42:58.372
to spend more time
with my grandchildren.

42:58.528 --> 42:59.887
My pension is already...

42:59.912 --> 43:01.212
I mean, maybe I can sell my house

43:01.237 --> 43:02.600
and buy one of those
little condos or...

43:02.625 --> 43:04.395
This is way too big a decision

43:04.420 --> 43:08.290
to make over one bad class. Okay?

43:09.058 --> 43:11.125
Don't rush into it.

43:13.955 --> 43:15.742
I'd...

43:16.012 --> 43:18.715
No. It's impossible.

43:19.813 --> 43:20.899
Why?

43:21.002 --> 43:22.230
Because...

43:23.326 --> 43:24.716
um...

43:25.287 --> 43:28.390
because it's too late, I'm too old.

43:30.273 --> 43:34.010
Thank you for... trying.

43:45.239 --> 43:46.694
Thank you.

43:57.405 --> 43:59.172
Why are you leaving, Mrs. Carol?

43:59.301 --> 44:01.803
Um, you're gonna have a sub today.

44:01.924 --> 44:03.530
- Wont that be fun?
- Yeah.

44:03.555 --> 44:05.589
Do you have your ancestor stories?

44:06.108 --> 44:07.258
Good, you can tell the sub

44:07.283 --> 44:08.511
what We've been doing, okay?

44:08.551 --> 44:10.778
- Okay.
- Okay. Have a good day.

44:14.008 --> 44:16.477
Ms. Carol, Ms. Carol!

44:17.644 --> 44:21.447
Markell. Oh!

44:23.845 --> 44:25.877
Where are you going?

44:26.488 --> 44:28.878
I have to leave, okay?

44:29.801 --> 44:32.104
Are you coming back tomorrow?

44:32.587 --> 44:36.218
I'm not. I'm not coming
back at all this summer.

44:37.047 --> 44:39.560
But you'll miss me too much.

44:40.335 --> 44:41.762
Come here.

44:42.784 --> 44:44.179
Okay.

44:45.553 --> 44:47.604
Okay, look at me.

44:48.103 --> 44:50.727
- You're a good boy.
- Mm-hmm.

44:51.366 --> 44:54.034
Okay. Go on in.

44:54.116 --> 44:56.411
- Bye, Ms. Carol.
- Bye.

44:57.025 --> 44:59.027
Bye.

45:36.332 --> 45:39.952
So, all of the shovels were
just for digging the tunnel?

45:40.269 --> 45:42.437
Oh, yeah. I mean, I was in there.
I could see it.

45:42.462 --> 45:44.165
Too small for, like, a
normal-sized person?

45:44.190 --> 45:45.902
Ah, you fucking got jokes.

45:45.975 --> 45:47.073
Fucking asshole.

